Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.80,0:00:33.05,SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\c&HADADAD&}The world of Shinigami
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.92,0:00:33.05,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinigami literally means a "God of Death".
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.63,0:00:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! {\alpha&HFF&}A pair of sleeping skulls?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.02,0:00:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! A pair of sleeping skulls?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.21,0:00:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hate me for this, but I win again!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.54,0:00:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ryuk! {\alpha&HFF&}Wanna join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.97,0:00:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ryuk! Wanna join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.32,0:00:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come hang out with us for a change.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.66,0:00:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... {\alpha&HFF&}I'll pass...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.80,0:01:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I'll pass...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.68,0:01:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen for the voice of God and never guess you will...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.44,0:01:09.96,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't done anything but he said that he wanted to split up with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.96,0:01:11.89,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,So what happened, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.00,0:01:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-kun, {\alpha&HFF&}is there anything wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.35,0:01:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-kun, is there anything wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.26,0:01:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you translate the previous sentences into Japanese please?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.98,0:01:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow the voice of God and he shall calm the waves, and protect us from storms.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.23,0:01:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At around 11 o'clock today,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.89,0:01:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the city of Yokohama, Kanagawa prefecture, {\alpha&HFF&}a thirty year old man was found covered in blood at his apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.90,0:01:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the city of Yokohama, Kanagawa prefecture, a thirty year old man was found covered in blood at his apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.78,0:01:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kanagawa police are currently treating this case as a suspected homicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.99,0:01:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next on the news...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.58,0:01:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today in the district of Shibuya, Tokyo, {\alpha&HFF&}a 25 year old woman was gagged and killed by her live-in partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.79,0:01:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today in the district of Shibuya, Tokyo, a 25 year old woman was gagged and killed by her live-in partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.29,0:01:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,35 year old, Tofuji Naoki, is being held in custody charged with her murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.63,0:02:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Day after day...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.92,0:02:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's always the same news.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.77,0:02:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Completely... {\alpha&HFF&}pointless...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.42,0:02:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Completely... pointless...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.11,0:02:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This world is... {\alpha&HFF&}rotting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.77,0:02:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This world is... rotting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.69,0:02:16.69,SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs72\pos(365,359)}Rebirth
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.40,0:02:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another is the extinction of many species of life on the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.49,0:02:23.63,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,You seriously went to see that shit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.63,0:02:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Species are becoming extinct at a faster rate than has occurred...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.63,0:02:25.33,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a complete waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.33,0:02:28.75,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,You get the feeling that they're just trying to make money.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.84,0:03:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Death Note?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.94,0:03:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Literally translated as "a notebook of death".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.40,0:03:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"How to use"...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.33,0:03:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The human whose name is written in this note shall die"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.47,0:03:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a joke...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.34,0:03:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty sick though, it's no different to chain letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.14,0:03:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The human whose name is written in this note shall die"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously... I must be going insane...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.65,0:03:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"This note will not take effect unless the writer has the person's face in their mind when they write his/her name."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.52,0:03:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Therefore, {\alpha&HFF&}people sharing the same name will not be affected."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.55,0:03:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Therefore, people sharing the same name will not be affected."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:04:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"If the cause of death is written within 40 seconds of writing the person's name, it will happen as it is written".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.21,0:04:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"If the cause of death is not specified, by default, the person will die of a heart attack".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.51,0:04:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Should a cause of death be specified, a further 6 minutes and 40 seconds are granted to write any further details".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.36,0:04:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this means you can either kill them quickly or painfully, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quite a lot of detail to go into for a simple prank... {\alpha&HFF&}Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.98,0:04:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quite a lot of detail to go into for a simple prank... Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.11,0:04:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Writing a name causes someone to die...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.11,0:04:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Completely pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.60,0:04:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.97,0:04:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the off-chance that someone actually does die, {\alpha&HFF&}wouldn't that make me a murderer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.64,0:04:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the off-chance that someone actually does die, wouldn't that make me a murderer?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.45,0:05:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible. {\alpha&HFF&}It'd never happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.74,0:05:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible. It'd never happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.39,0:05:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The phantom killer who attacked six people in Shinjuku's business district yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.56,0:05:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,has now taken eight children and kindergarten teachers as hostages and is holed up in this nursery.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.01,0:05:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The police has identified the man as Otoharada Kurou, aged 42, unemployed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.53,0:05:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that they're about to begin negotiations...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.53,0:05:24.63,SILLYSIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35.59322\frz24\pos(373,279)\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}Otoharada Kurou
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.11,0:05:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to the book, he should have a heart attack in 40 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.67,0:05:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the present time, we don't have a lot of information.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.36,0:05:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't help but feel extremely concerned for the safety of the hostages.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.06,0:05:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.27,0:05:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all there is to report from the scene at this present moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.82,0:05:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.16,0:05:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you make of the current situation, Hashimoto-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.68,0:05:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, {\alpha&HFF&}all I can say is that we can only hope to resolve this situation quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.72,0:05:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, all I can say is that we can only hope to resolve this situation quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.62,0:05:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing happened after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.49,0:05:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that was to be expected.
