Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.77,0:05:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! Wait a minute! {\alpha&HFF&}Something appears to be happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.07,0:06:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! Wait a minute! Something appears to be happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.90,0:06:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hostages are coming out! {\alpha&HFF&}They all appear to be unharmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.25,0:06:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hostages are coming out! They all appear to be unharmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.87,0:06:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The police are rushing the building as the hostages exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has the culprit been apprehended?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.22,0:06:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.05,0:06:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've just heard that the culprit was found dead in the nursery!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.26,0:06:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it looks like the culprit is dead!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.97,0:06:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.98,0:06:20.02,SILLYSIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs45.762712\c&H000000&\2c&HFFFFFF&\frz319.065\pos(194,255)\3c&HFFFFFF&}Otoharada Kurou
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.02,0:06:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The riot police have denied shooting the man.
