Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.67,0:06:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.24,0:06:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a long shot, but if this is the real thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.84,0:06:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to test it again.
