Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.10,0:07:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if they're too infamous, {\alpha&HFF&}there's the possibility that their deaths may initially be covered up...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.73,0:07:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if they're too infamous, there's the possibility that their deaths may initially be covered up...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.54,0:07:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to see results now!
