Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.49,0:07:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Where possible I should avoid people I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.02,0:07:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then again, I shouldn't be too bothered, {\alpha&HFF&}nobody will care if one or two guys like him disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.21,0:07:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then again, I shouldn't be too bothered, nobody will care if one or two guys like him disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.29,0:07:41.23,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going to the arcade again on my way home with this!
