Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.83,0:07:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! That stupid old hag isn't here to pick me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.07,0:07:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez.. {\alpha&HFF&}Thinking about this really makes you realize just how many people the world would actually be better off without.
