Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.63,0:08:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Takuo-san for you, you've certainly bagged another hottie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.20,0:08:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The name's Shibuimaru Takuo, but you can call me Shibutaku.
