Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.72,0:09:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, you really fucked up this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.40,0:09:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on, didn't you cheat a second Death Note out of the Shinigami Overlord?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.49,0:09:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you lost both of 'em?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.78,0:09:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do ya even know where ya dropped it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.14,0:09:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The human world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.36,0:09:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.61,0:10:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.00,0:10:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty early today, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.71,0:10:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back, mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.16,0:10:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.51,0:10:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you want the results of the national mock exams, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.51,0:10:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.70,0:10:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Number one again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.57,0:10:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really tried hard, didn't you, Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.57,0:10:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess. {\alpha&HFF&}I'm going to study in my room, so don't interrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.86,0:10:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess. I'm going to study in my room, so don't interrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.57,0:10:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.09,0:10:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yes, Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:10:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.35,0:11:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can ask for whatever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.89,0:11:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing really, mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.02,0:11:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already got what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.27,0:11:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see that you've taken quite a shine to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.66,0:11:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.27,0:11:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Ryuk, the Shinigami who dropped that notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.59,0:11:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Judging by that face of yours earlier, {\alpha&HFF&}it seems you've already realized that that is no ordinary notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.72,0:11:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Judging by that face of yours earlier, it seems you've already realized that that is no ordinary notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.43,0:11:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Shinigami, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.17,0:12:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not surprised, Ryuk...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.46,0:12:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, {\alpha&HFF&}I've been waiting for you, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.10,0:12:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, I've been waiting for you, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.14,0:12:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ohh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.84,0:12:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already realized that this Shinigami's notebook is real.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.10,0:12:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And after seeing its results, {\alpha&HFF&}I can act with certainty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.68,0:12:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And after seeing its results, I can act with certainty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.91,0:12:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. {\alpha&HFF&}You surprise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.84,0:12:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. You surprise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.26,0:12:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the past, I've heard of instances where a Death Note has appeared in the human world,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.90,0:12:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you're the first person to have written this many names in just five days.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.87,0:12:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, people are too frightened to write as much as this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.77,0:12:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already prepared myself, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.16,0:12:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knowingly used a Shinigami's notebook, {\alpha&HFF&}and now a Shinigami has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.45,0:12:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knowingly used a Shinigami's notebook, and now a Shinigami has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.77,0:12:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll happen to me? {\alpha&HFF&}Are you going to take my soul?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.32,0:12:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll happen to me? Are you going to take my soul?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.67,0:12:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.87,0:12:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this some kind of fantasy created by humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.25,0:12:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to do anything to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.93,0:13:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The moment that notebook fell to this world, it became the property of the human world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.63,0:13:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, {\alpha&HFF&}that notebook belongs to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.77,0:13:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, that notebook belongs to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.67,0:13:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.99,0:13:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want it, you can pass it to someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.96,0:13:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I reserve the right to erase your memory of the Death Note if you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.76,0:13:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're telling me that there's really no trade-off for using the Death Note?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.79,0:13:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you insist on knowing, {\alpha&HFF&}there is the fear and suffering that is faced only by those humans who use Death Notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.66,0:13:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you insist on knowing, there is the fear and suffering that is faced only by those humans who use Death Notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.18,0:13:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And finally, when you die, {\alpha&HFF&}it falls to me to write your name in my Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.79,0:13:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And finally, when you die, it falls to me to write your name in my Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.02,0:13:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't assume that a human who's used the Death Note can go to Heaven or Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.11,0:13:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.81,0:13:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have something to look forward to when you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.69,0:14:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.04,0:14:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. Answer it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.03,0:14:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.98,0:14:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've brought you some apples. {\alpha&HFF&}The neighbours brought them round to share.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.69,0:14:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've brought you some apples. The neighbours brought them round to share.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.85,0:14:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it so dark in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.36,0:14:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll ruin your eyesight you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? {\alpha&HFF&}Can't mother see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.20,0:14:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&HFF&}_
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.20,0:14:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? Can't mother see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.67,0:14:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That used to be my notebook, {\alpha&HFF&}so as the current user you're the only one who can see me, and of course the only one who can hear me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.75,0:14:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That used to be my notebook, so as the current user you're the only one who can see me, {\alpha&HFF&}and of course the only one who can hear me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.13,0:14:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That used to be my notebook, so as the current user you're the only one who can see me, and of course the only one who can hear me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.20,0:14:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Death Note is the bond that ties you, the human, to me, Ryuk, the Shinigami, so to speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.03,0:14:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mmm, nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.45,0:14:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I ask you one more thing.. {\alpha&HFF&}Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.03,0:14:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I ask you one more thing.. Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.97,0:14:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.42,0:14:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, apples in the human world are damn good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.74,0:14:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're.. how to say it..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.03,0:14:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"juicy"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.58,0:15:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.38,0:15:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't pick you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.09,0:15:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just happened to drop the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.87,0:15:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, did you think you'd been picked because you're smart or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.03,0:15:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.19,0:15:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It just happened to fall around here, and you just happened to pick it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.06,0:15:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I wrote it in the most popular human language, English.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.67,0:15:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why did you drop it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.73,0:15:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You went through the whole trouble of writing down instructions, so don't tell me you just happened to drop it by accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.67,0:15:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you say... {\alpha&HFF&}because I was bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.92,0:15:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you say... because I was bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.08,0:15:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bored?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.02,0:15:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is that most Shinigami haven't got much to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.11,0:15:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They mainly sleep or gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.95,0:15:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try writing any names in your book, {\alpha&HFF&}and they'll laugh at you for trying too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.82,0:15:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try writing any names in your book, and they'll laugh at you for trying too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.27,0:15:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you write the name of someone living in the Shinigami world, they won't die, {\alpha&HFF&}and it's no fun killing humans from the Shinigami world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.72,0:15:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you write the name of someone living in the Shinigami world, they won't die, and it's no fun killing humans from the Shinigami world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.24,0:16:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I figured it'd be more fun in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.62,0:16:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you seem to have written quite a few names here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.15,0:16:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why did you only write the cause of death for the guy that was run over by a dump truck?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.11,0:16:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't write the cause of death, the victim dies of a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.81,0:16:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the best thing about the Death Note, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.78,0:16:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already begun to exhaust the list of high profile criminals, and I'm gradually including people that commit less serious crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.72,0:16:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what does that achieve?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.84,0:16:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how stupid people are, they'll eventually realize that someone is wiping out these criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.87,0:16:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to let the world know of my existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.55,0:16:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That there is someone who can, and will, pass righteous judgement!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.84,0:16:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what do you plan to achieve by passing this "righteous judgement"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.29,0:16:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why bother?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.65,0:16:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because... {\alpha&HFF&}I'm also bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.35,0:16:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because... I'm also bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.64,0:17:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, at first I didn't believe it, {\alpha&HFF&}but that notebook has a kind of magic that compels humans to try it at least once.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.06,0:17:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, at first I didn't believe it, but that notebook has a kind of magic that compels humans to try it at least once.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.61,0:17:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I k-killed them...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.96,0:17:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.86,0:17:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a life. The consequences can't be light.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.35,0:17:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I have the right to pass judgements on others?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.96,0:17:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But wait, it's not like that. {\alpha&HFF&}This is what I've always thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.93,0:17:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But wait, it's not like that. This is what I've always thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.05,0:17:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This world is rotting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.18,0:17:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who are rotting deserve to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.25,0:17:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.89,0:17:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone has to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.73,0:17:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sacrificing their own life and soul, {\alpha&HFF&}because the world just can't continue like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.28,0:17:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sacrificing their own life and soul, because the world just can't continue like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.92,0:17:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If someone else had picked up this notebook, {\alpha&HFF&}would they be able to erase all the unnecessary people from this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.50,0:17:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If someone else had picked up this notebook, would they be able to erase all the unnecessary people from this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.18,0:17:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.37,0:17:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can... {\alpha&HFF&}I can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.98,0:18:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can... I can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.85,0:18:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, I'm the only one who can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.53,0:18:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it. I'll use the Death Note..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.98,0:18:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To change the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.23,0:18:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I began to think of it as "tidying up the world", and continued to write down the names of the most monstrous criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.29,0:18:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually no one will be able to commit a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.52,0:18:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, {\alpha&HFF&}behind the fact that deserving criminals are dying of heart attacks,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.52,0:19:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, behind the fact that deserving criminals are dying of heart attacks,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.52,0:19:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll gradually start killing of those who cause problems for innocent people, through illness and accidental death.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.42,0:19:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way it's certain that the world will become a better place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.45,0:19:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll have created a world filled with those I've judged to be kind and hard working.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.22,0:19:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do that, you'll be the only fucked up person left.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.70,0:19:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, Ryuk?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.86,0:19:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm probably the most virtuous student in the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.48,0:19:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.35,0:19:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll become the God of my new world!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.86,0:19:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it! Humans are... {\alpha&HFF&}so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.21,0:19:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it! Humans are... so much fun!
